    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >体验全面演进的经典冒险游戏！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1983 的经典横向卷轴平台游戏《Montezuma’s Revenge》以 2.5D 风格闪亮回归，而且现在 Pedro 的冒险格局比以往更加宏大，有 100 个诡异房间等着你来探索！值此 40 周年纪念日之际，这款曾经的未竟之作如今全血复活，完美展现了原创者 Robert Jaeger 的完整愿景。这一次，你可以在男性和女性探险家（Pedro 或他的姊妹 Rosita）之间进行选择，然后深入危险的废墟，探寻未知宝藏！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101230/extras/fe60dd8d7b9746cb2c81d6c5e9fac0e0.poster.avif?t=1738808497\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101230/extras/fe60dd8d7b9746cb2c81d6c5e9fac0e0.webm?t=1738808497\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101230/extras/fe60dd8d7b9746cb2c81d6c5e9fac0e0.mp4?t=1738808497\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Montezuma’s Revenge: The 40th Anniversary Edition》是重新制作的全新版本，采用动感十足的 3D 画面，同时保留 1983 年原版的 2D 游戏风格。一路奔跑、跳跃和攀爬，穿过诡异棘手的密室，以收集贵重的文物，避开凶险的陷阱和凶恶的敌人，找到钥匙继续前进，并在一场最终决战中活下来，然后带着你到手的财宝……还有你的性命逃出来。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101230/extras/114f92d1a764064d0f0dd3d32aa578a2.poster.avif?t=1738808497\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101230/extras/114f92d1a764064d0f0dd3d32aa578a2.webm?t=1738808497\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101230/extras/114f92d1a764064d0f0dd3d32aa578a2.mp4?t=1738808497\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏特点：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在富于冒险精神的男性和女性主角之间进行选择！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索 100 间诡异棘手的密室，里面布满陷阱、宝藏和游荡的歹徒。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一边解开废墟的众多谜团，一边收集贵重的文物！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >享受以 2.5D 风格重新构想的复古美学。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >重新体验一款永恒的经典电子游戏，畅玩迄今为止它最完整的版本！</p></li></ul>",
